{"tid":1539601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求入院既小朋友唔好亂講嘢，安靜休息","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:33:16.000Z","uid":81555,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ffd6a59ebe548cb1593139f69e58b13792199b7","tid":1539601,"uid":81555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:10:29.000Z","msg":"入咗院既小朋友，<br />\n坐喺你側邊嗰位既扮同你做朋友傾計<br />\n<br />\n跪求唔好上當😭😭<br />\n佢喺你側邊講話同你同立場，唔明你點諗<br />\n<br />\n唔該你唔好解釋，唔好亂講自己喺邊度整親，<br />\n去過邊度旅行<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記自己點解會入院<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身邊既姑娘多次想叫你安靜D,但係你都繼續同佢傾<br />\n<br />\n防人之心不可無啊😭😭😭😭<br />\n<br />\n安靜休息啦好嗎，有咩需要好多醫生姑娘會幫你同你傾計😭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩同各位家長講聲，好好勸小朋友休息同保持警覺😭😭😭😭"},{"pid":"712e342196989acacaa54acc68e2059ddc55cccf","tid":1539601,"uid":219835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:11:27.000Z","msg":"tui <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425bceb7fcb2f5f4a624a603fb0965493c43f8ff","tid":1539601,"uid":81555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"推，唔該探病時間同小朋友講啊"},{"pid":"0e08a05ea5a39ee8ba696883bbe06688558db64f","tid":1539601,"uid":192758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}